response.original_title: EVE Not Made to Be Subtle
response.overview: Main Event Empress" Sammii Jayne defeated Candyfloss by submission. Following the match, Rhia O'Reilly announced that Sammii Jayne would have to defend the Pro-Wrestling:EVE Championship or she would be strip of the title. She was informed that she would be defending the championship in a rumble and she would be the first entrant.
response.title: EVE Not Made to Be Subtle
